```plantuml
@startuml KuangRD_Autonomous-Driving

actor User

box "ROS-Based Autonomous Driving System" #LightBlue
    participant "Waypoint Loader\n(Node)" as WaypointLoader
    participant "Waypoint Updater\n(Node)" as WaypointUpdater
    participant "DBW Controller\n(Node)" as DBWController
    participant "Traffic Light Detector\n(Node)" as TrafficLightDetector
    participant "Simulator/Car" as Simulator
end box

User -> Simulator: Start Simulation
Simulator -> WaypointLoader: Load Waypoints
WaypointLoader -> WaypointUpdater: Send Loaded Waypoints
WaypointUpdater -> DBWController: Update Waypoints
DBWController -> Simulator: Control Commands (Drive-by-Wire)

Simulator -> TrafficLightDetector: Send Camera Image
TrafficLightDetector -> TrafficLightDetector: Process Image (TensorFlow/Keras)
TrafficLightDetector -> WaypointUpdater: Update Waypoints based on Traffic Light
TrafficLightDetector -> Simulator: Detection Results

note right of TrafficLightDetector
  Traffic Light Classification:
  - CNN Model
  - CUDA Acceleration
end note

User -> DBWController: Adjust PID Parameters
DBWController -> DBWController: Execute PID Control

note over WaypointLoader, TrafficLightDetector
  Communication via JSON Messages
end note

@enduml
```